name: Down To Earth (Haiyuna)
description:
This game was made at the end of our first year of school.

The goal of our game was to help people in the differents levels by doing interactions.

Since it's our very first game there may have little bugs, or somethings not really good but I want to keep a backup of this game on the internet !

This game was made by Maxime Vantorre, Paul Bernard, Théo Leicht and Anissa Bouchakour.
